title: 098: Famous Workout Partners, Ridiculous Exercises, Binge & Stress Eating and Adam's Dating Timeline
description: It is Sal, Adam & Justin's favorite time of the week... answering PumpHead questions (Instagram @mindpump). This week they answer questions about their dream workout partner, the most ridiculous exercises they have witnessed, how to help binge and stress eating clients and the icing on the cake, dating advice from Adam.
